node.text: I think my family would run for their lives if I tried to cut hair..

😂😂😂😂 Such a fun post.
And I love your dress, where is it from?
Do you know that peacock 🦚 feathers are known as unlucky in Eastern Europe? I love peacocks- such beautiful creatures

Have you guys tried the at home salon yet? Usually involves two kids pulling my hair and smashing brushes in my eyes. The experience is painful and I come out looking worse than I arrived but I can pay in kisses so I’ll give it a 10/10. .
.
. 
Have you guys tried any at home hair fixes? How’d they go? I’m still trying to convince my husband and son that I could cut their hair but they don’t believe me. Probably best. I’d want to give them a fade and a Nike swoosh or something and since I don’t know how to do either it would probably end up with scrubby bald patches. But who’s going to see anyway?! It’d make a great story and I do love a good story. 😅😂😇
.
.
.
Earrings (new collection) @houseofrajput 
Dress (past season) @simoneirani .
.
.
Ps I know I have a tail sticking out of my head. Framing wasn’t exact on this one. Always wanted to be a mermaid though. 🧜🏻‍♀️
@aprilnerford oh yes! Both my kids love it. I added some colorful brushes I found at Daiso as the wood ones hurt too much. I’m nervous to add real make up. How’d that go?

@sabrinasikora haha it’s a work in progress. I fought it as long as I could!!! Finally had a good full week of home schooling so I caved. Got the non-toxic child friendly stuff from Carrotsticks & Cravings Robertson Quay - couple lippy’s, blushes and eyeshadows
This is Jaiden’s FAVOURITE toy (once I added some “real make up” 🙄🙄🙄
Love it and the print of that gorgeous dress!! 😍
Hahah. Love it.
Love everything in this frame! From kids toys, to pink blusher, to our earrings and this dress! What a fabulous look you put up! Stunning is the word (even at home) 💛😘
OMG stop we have this and the amount of times we play with it. 😆 Zhanna is trying to upgrade to the real stuff now though. Love your whole look babes.
This is fab! My hair gets done daily by them and alot of pretend make up 💛
You are always so perfect! your at home salon is spot on! I have mine and you can see the fun and fails in my videos 🤣😅🙈
They have nothing to lose! 🤷‍♀️🤣

🌈
🌕

Looking fab! No hair cutting going on here! 😘
So beautiful ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️
I am loving these snaps. So much fu gorgeous girl.
I cut and DIY dye my hair when when we arent in lockdown..... and not doing it now simply because there is no point 🤣
